1. create feature/update branch: git branch <branch-name>
2. go to branch to create changes: git checkout <branch-name>
3. create changes, build and test: jekyll serve
4. stage & commit changes: git commit -a -m 'commit message'
5. go back to master to merge: git checkout master
6. merge changes to master: git merge <branch-name>
7. delete feature branch: git branch -d <branch-name>
8. push changes to github: git push origin master
